Class SourceTreePreparationProcessor

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    PreCompilationProcessor

    public class SourceTreePreparationProcessor
extends AbstractSourceTreePreparationProcessor
    Pre compilation processor responsible for preparing source file with imports (deep, imports of imports). It's saving for all sources:
    • modification date
    • imports list

      • prepareWhenExpired

        protected void prepareWhenExpired(LessSource source,
                                  Set<String> preparedSourcesPaths)
        Description copied from class: AbstractSourceTreePreparationProcessor
        Prepares a source file to the compilation process. Called only when source expired (determines by checker). If this method should prepare the source import, then you must call AbstractSourceTreePreparationProcessor.prepare(LessSource, Set).
        Specified by:
        prepareWhenExpired in class AbstractSourceTreePreparationProcessor
        Parameters:
        source - the source file.
        preparedSourcesPaths - set with prepared sources paths.
